cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI 

This paper deals with the anonymization of network traces for privacy concerns and evaluates the impact of anonymization on the utility of data for anomaly detection. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computer Security and Networking (cs.CR, cs.NI). Additionally, the paper uses quantitative evaluation and analysis techniques, which are related to Machine Learning (cs.LG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
